                <head>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Editor’s Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>—No record of this conversation has been found other than <persName
                        corresp="#p_TJV1">Truman</persName>’s statement at the Ninth Plenary
                    Meeting, <pb facs="0566" n="380" xml:id="pg_380"/> July 25, “that the Secretary
                    of State had talked with the Poles and expected to have more talks” (see <hi
                        rend="italic">post</hi>, <ref target="#pg_382">page 382</ref>). Cf.
                        <persName corresp="#p_TJV1">Truman</persName>, <hi rend="italic">Year of
                        Decisions</hi>, page 388.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
